thread.title: Suess Microtec receives large volume order for lithography projection scanners
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Suess Microtec receives large volume order for lithography projection scanners | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Suess Microtec receives large volume order for lithography projection scanners
text:
Sept 24 Suess Microtec AG :
* Receives large volume order for lithography projection scanners
* Order volume is in high single-digit million euro range
* Order includes multiple DSC300 Gen2 projection scanners, which are produced at company's facility in Corona, USA Source text for Eikon: (Gdynia Newsroom)
